Package wibiral.tim.javachr.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AlreadyDefinedException
    This message is thrown by the rules if the user tries to set a new body/guard if the body/guard is already set.
    EmptyRuleSetException
    This method gets thrown by the ConstraintHandler if the set of rules given to the constructor is empty.
    RuleSetIsBlockedException
    Is thrown if someone tries to add a rule after a handler with the rule set was created.
